     9→/// A source of key-values.
    10→///
    11→/// The source may be a single pair, a set of pairs, or a filter over a set of pairs.
    12→/// Use the [`VisitSource`](trait.VisitSource.html) trait to inspect the structured data
    13→/// in a source.
